title: 612. 10 Takeaways from Week 10
itunes:title: 612. 10 Takeaways from Week 10
description:
Daniel Jeremiah, Bucky Brooks and Rhett Lewis look back at the weekend and pick ten storylines that stood out from Week 10 of the NFL season. To start off, the guys look at how the Patriots beat the Ravens with the Ravens play style (1:10). Next, the trio discuss the Dolphins defense and how the team befuddled Chargers QB Justin Herbert in their matchup (5:46). Later, the guys analyze the Raiders after they bullied the Broncos (20:54). To wrap up the show, DJ, Bucky and Rhett talk about why you shouldn't count the Giants out as their playoff hopes and ability to win the division are still alive (37:18). All that and more in this packed episode.
